  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This extension applies to the Endpoint resource and is used to represent routing HL7 V2 message payload details associated with an endpoint. This content allows a sender using these endpoint details to include Receiving Application (MSH-5) information in HL7 V2 messages sent via this channel which allow correct delivery within the receiving system."] ; # 
